text: Örebro HK is an ice hockey club in the town of Örebro in Sweden. The club was established in 1990 as HC Örebro 90, before changing name in 2005. In 2013, Örebro HK qualifyed for the Swedish Hockey League. ==Other websites== * Official website Category:1990 establishments in Sweden Category:Ice hockey teams in Sweden Category:Sport in Örebro
